Here is the daily activity digest for #{@region_name} on #{(Time.now - 1.day).strftime('%m/%d/%Y')}.

Machine Comments

- @machine_comments.each do |item|
  = item[:location_name]
  = " (https://pinballmap.com/map?by_location_id=#{item[:location_id]})"
  = item[:machine_name]
  = item[:comment]
  = item[:user_name]

Machine Removals

- @machine_removals.each do |item|
  = item[:location_name]
  = " (https://pinballmap.com/map?by_location_id=#{item[:location_id]})"
  = item[:machine_name]
  = item[:user_name]

Pictures Added

- @pictures_added.each do |item|
  = item[:location_name]
  = " (https://pinballmap.com/map?by_location_id=#{item[:location_id]})"
  = item[:user_name]

High Scores

- @high_scores.each do |item|
  = item[:location_name]
  = " (https://pinballmap.com/map?by_location_id=#{item[:location_id]})"
  = item[:machine_name]
  = number_with_delimiter(item[:high_score])
  = item[:user_name]
